			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">Centuries-Old Shark Teeth Suggest Brazil’s Ocean Is Less Resilient Today</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Researchers used shark teeth from a 13th-century fishing site in southern Brazil to get a picture of how the ecosystem has changed.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/sarah-sloat/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Sarah Sloat</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
