						<li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share tagmanager" title="Share by Email" href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0ACenturies-Old Shark Teeth Suggest Brazil’s Ocean Is Less Resilient Today%0D%0AResearchers used shark teeth from a 13th-century fishing site in southern Brazil to get a picture of how the ecosystem has changed.%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/news/centuries-old-shark-teeth-suggest-brazils-ocean-is-less-resilient-today/" target="_blank"><span>Share by Email</span></a></li>



					</ul>
